snippet.title: THE DETECTIVE CHAPTERS: PART ONE - Debut Trailer
snippet.description:
Info: https://mayhemgamesusa.com/    
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/981660/The_Detective_Chapters_Part_One/    
About: The exhaust fumes were heavy in the air to the point of suffocation. Even though the garage door was closed, you instinctively opened it when you heard the rumble of the engine coming from the other side. Your father was dead...
